o many attractions that we have kept this day to yourself. Try some sumptuous local food or visit the National Museum to understand the history of Singapore or Botanical Gardens. We meet in the evening for the farewell dinner.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"5\" title=\"Day 5:Departure day\"]Time to bid adieu. Check out from hotel and transfer to Changi International Airport\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item]<strong>End of this memorable tour.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/timeline]\";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Terms and Conditions\";s:7:\"content\";s:838:\"1. To confirm your spot, you can pay a deposit of 6900 INR (this is a non-refundable amount)\r\n2. You will have to pay 10,100 INR before 25th December 2016 for us to proceed with the bookings.\r\n3. Rest of the amount : 10,000/- has to be paid before 1st January 2017.\r\n\r\n<strong>Cancellation policy: </strong>\r\n1. 6900 INR deposit is non-refundable.\r\n2. 75% of the remaining amount will be refunded, if you cancel your participation before 60 days of the tour date.\r\n3. 50% of the remaining amount will be refunded, if you cancel your participation before 40 days of the tour date.\r\n4. 25% of the remaining amount will be refunded, if you cancel your participation before 20 days of the tour date.\r\n5. 15% of the remaining amount will be refunded, if you cancel your participation before 15 days of the tour date.\r\n6. No refund afterwards.\";}}}'),(3580,1628,'_tax_status','taxable'),(3581,1628,'_tax_class',''),(3582,1628,'slide_template','default'),(3583,1628,'tour_booking_periods','a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:11:\"exact_dates\";a:1:{i:0;s:10:\"2017-01-25\";}s:5:\"limit\";s:2:\"15\";s:10:\"spec_price\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"mode\";s:11:\"exact-dates\";s:4:\"type\";s:1:\"1\";s:4:\"from\";s:10:\"2017-01-25\";s:2:\"to\";s:10:\"2017-01-25\";}}'),(3584,1628,'_product_version','2.6.14'),(3585,1628,'_variable_tour','no'),(3586,1628,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(3587,1628,'_edit_lock','1491942190:1'),(3588