eline_item item_number=\"2\" title=\"Day 2\"] Early Morning wakeup and <strong>Celebrate Holi</strong> in the camp (Play, eat and celebrate). Later in the afternoon <strong>start River Rafting </strong>from Shivpuri down the Ganges to NIM Beach Rishikesh for around 16 kms<strong>.</strong><strong> </strong>Hit some of the most splashing and enjoyable rapids like<strong> Three Blind mice, Cross Fire, Sweet Sixteen, Body Surfing, Return To Sender, Roller Coaster, Tea Off, Golf Course, Club House, Cash Flow, Initiation, Double Trouble And Hilton. </strong>One can try<strong> </strong><strong>Body Surfing </strong>in this section. In the later part, we float across the past temples and ashrams and Ghats enjoying the riverbank life along the holy river.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item][timeline_item item_number=\"3\" title=\"Day 3]\"]Have morning tea. Pack your bags and after breakfast, start for the optional <b>Jungle Trek to the Neer Waterfall</b><b> (4 kms approx both sides) </b>Arrive in Rishikesh. Tour terminates with the flash back memories.\r\n\r\n[/timeline_item]<strong>End of this memorable tour.</strong>\r\n\r\n[/timeline]\";}i:1;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Location\";s:7:\"content\";s:153:\"<pre><code></code>[google_map_embed src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1PDRbfivSbvgf6cV9Xi3Dz8gOMYU\" height=\"400\" width_mode=\"box-width\"]</pre>\";}i:2;a:2:{s:5:\"title\";s:20:\"Terms and Conditions\";s:7:\"content\";s:1253:\"<strong>Terms and conditions:</strong> Expedition cost: 1545 USD\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>To confirm your spot, you can pay 100 USD (this is a non-refundable amount)</li>\r\n 	<li>You will have to pay a deposit of 650 USD before 1st January 2017 for us to proceed with the bookings.</li>\r\n 	<li>Rest of the amount : has to be paid before 1st Feb 2017.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>Cancellation policy:</strong>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>100 USD is non-refundable.</li>\r\n 	<li>95% of your booking amount will be refunded, if you cancel your participation before 75 days of 