 is one of the prominent destination for travel enthusiasts because of Himalayas, gorging waterfalls, snowcapped mountains, monasteries, flora and fauna. Not to forget the authentic momos and sumptuous thupka.\r\n\r\nDarjeeling on the other hand is surrounded by emerald-green tea plantations and towered over by the majestic Khangchendzonga (8598m).\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered tours-tabs__table\" style=\"height: 233px;\" width=\"862\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>START  and END LOCATION</strong></td>\r\n<td>Bagdogra Airport</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>START DATE</strong></td>\r\n<td> 18-March-2017</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>END DATE</strong></td>\r\n<td>24-March-2017</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Duration</strong></td>\r\n<td> 7 Days/6 Nights</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>GROUP SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td>12</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Price</strong></td>\r\n<td>21,999 INR</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>PLACES COVERED</strong></td>\r\n<td>Namchi, Pelling and Darjeeling.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>INCLUDED</strong></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"height: 62px;\" width=\"300\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Accommodations</td>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Local transportation</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Group Leader</td>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Pick up and drop to the airport</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><b>NOT INCLUDED</b></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"height: 62px;\" width=\"300\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Flights or train tickets</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Meals not mentioned</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Travel/ Health Insurance</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Anything not mentioned in inclusions</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td