/jpeg',0),(1628,1,'2016-12-01 11:36:37','2016-12-01 11:36:37','<strong>Singapore on a Shoestring Group Trip</strong>\r\n\r\nBe a part of our <a class=\"_58cn\" href=\"http://yourholidayagent.com/about-us/\" data-ft=\"{&quot;tn&quot;:&quot;*N&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:104}\">#20before40</a> campaign to cover 20 countries before you turn 40.\r\n\r\nOur aim is to promote backpacking and solo travel culture amongst the Youth of India. All our trips are focussed on enabling the participants who join us to learn the tricks of travelling solo, backpacking and to travel in budget.\r\n\r\nDescribed as a microcosm of Asia, it is no secret that Singapore is expensive, and not just by South East Asian standards, either. You could easily blow through a huge budget while in this city-state, but there is actually no need to break the bank. We have a good news for you. Join us in this exclusive shoestring and fun tour of Singapore.\r\n<table class=\"table table-bordered tours-tabs__table\" style=\"height: 233px; width: 860px;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>START LOCATION</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">Singapore Airport</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>END LOCATION</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">Singapore Airport</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>START DATE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\"> 25-Jan-2017</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>END DATE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">29-Jan-2017</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>Duration</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">5 Days/4 Nights</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>GROUP SIZE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">4 to 15</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>PRICE</strong></td>\r\n<td style=\"w