d in this land of High Passes.\n<table class=\"table table-bordered tours-tabs__table\" style=\"height: 233px; width: 860px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>START and End LOCATION</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">Leh Airport</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>Trip Dates</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">11th June to 17th June</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>END DATE</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">29-Jan-2017</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>Duration</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">5 Days/4 Nights</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>GROUP SIZE</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">4 to 15</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>PRICE</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">400 USD / 27,000 INR</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>HIGHLIGHTS</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">Sentosa Island, Sky Park, Little India, China Town, Gardens by the bay.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><strong>INCLUDED</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"height: 62px;\" width=\"300\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Shared Accommodations</td>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Local transportation</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Pick up and drop to the airport</td>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]All Permits</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Everyday Breakfast</td>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]2 Dinners</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"on\"]Unlimited Fun</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><b>NOT INCLUDED</b></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"height: 62px;\" width=\"300\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Flights or bus transportation to/from Leh</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Meals not mentioned</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Entry Tickets</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Travel/ Health Insurance</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Tips for guides</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[icon_tick state=\"off\"]Anything not mentioned in inclusions</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 131.640625px;\"><b>Contact</b></td>\n<td style=\"width: 713.359375px;\">+91 9731587004, +91 9818141240</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\nLocal drivers are used throughout the tour but your Group Leader will be with you the entire time.\n\n<strong>Physical Level</strong>: While the tour itself is not very strenuous, please note that it can involve the following: somewhat long days, a good amount of walking, long journeys by private vehicle, early morning wake-ups and other similarly challenging scenarios.\n\n<strong>Subject to Change</strong>: Please keep in mind that the above itinerary and activities are subject to change. Travel sometime involves unexpected situations so things might need to be re-arranged at times. However, it is important to remember that travel is all about the journey, and so even the unexpected situations we may face should be treated as part of the overall experience!\n\n<strong>Accommodation</strong>: Prices are based on the sharing of rooms and single members of the group will typically be put together. We will be using guest houses and Swiss tents/camps that offer comfortable facilities. While we always do our best to secure as many rooms with separate beds as possible, sometime two members of the group might have to share a large bed. But that’s all part of the adventure and we guarantee we’ll have a blast anyway.','Leh Ladhakh Group Trip','<table style=\"width: 228.234375px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 110px;\">6 Nights/7 Days,</td>\n<td style=\"width: 103.234375px;\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 110px;\">11-June-2017,</td>\n<td style=\"width: 103.234375px;\">17th-June-2017</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 110px;\">Group Size:</td>\n<td style=\"width: 103.234375px;\"> 4-15</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>','inherit','closed','closed','','1896-autosave-v1','','','2017-04-04 21:06:18','2017-04-04 21:06:18','',1896,'http://yourholidayagent.com/1896-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1915,1,'2017-04-11 20:03:28','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2017-04-11 20:03:28','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://yourholidayagent.com/?p=1915',0,'post','',0),(1918,1,'2017-04-11 20:13:13','2017-04-11 20:13:13','','Roaming-Clan','','inherit','open','closed','','roaming-clan','','','2017-04-11 20:13:13','2017-04-11 20:13:13','',0,'http://yourholidayagent.com/wp-content/uploads/Roaming-Clan.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1919,1,'2017-04-12 09:09:20','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','closed','','','','','2017-04-12 09:09:20','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://yourholidayagent.com/?p=1919',0,'post','',0);
